Author: Hubezoo
Title: [ANN] Unagold Token: Quantum Blockchain and the Internetwork of the Future
Body: http://www.hubezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/cropped-Hubezoo-Logo-e1513447116263-1.png  The Power of the Quantum Blockchain  Hubezoo protcol is the first quantum blockchain.  With quantum applications, online platforms are able to accelerate functionality and users.    Scaleable: Quantum applications are expansive, allowing the blockchain to "layer" and work with multiple interactions Sustainable: Our Unagold token is open and with multi - faceted applications, can interchange with all other types of tokens and data Organizes Big Data: Hubezoo organizes information by category and type, changing misinformation into transparency Hyperspeeds Searches Creates More Interactivity: We integrate a social media network with e-commerce and information, developing a user friendly grid Expanded Transactions: Hubezoo is able to hyperspeed transactions and direct / navigate how these are used online  The Network Where Everyone Wins  We create a multi - faceted application using quantum technologies and blockchain.  With the use of AI, advanced technologies and layered approaches through our internetwork, we offer accessibility to all users.  Our technology is divided into 22 niche hubs, all which interface with layers of social media, e-commerce and big data, creating the internetwork of the future.    http://www.hubezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Holograph.jpeg  The Unagold Token  http://www.hubezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/unagold-flower-of-life-cropped.png  Unagold is a multi - layered token, hyperspeeding transactions by working with quantum applications.  Unagold provides a revolving door, creating fluidity of transactions while expanding types of transactions to smart contracts and big data.    http://www.hubezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Unagold-revolving-door.png  As the Hubezoo network expands, Unagold will be applicable to different walks of life.  Unagold tokens which are specific to unique transactions will be applied.  Quantum applications allow the Unagold token to function uniquely based on types of transaction.    http://www.hubezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/UNAGOLD-interlink.png  Benefits of Unagold Token  http://www.hubezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/bankezoo-benefits-table-2-1.png  PreSale Information  http://www.hubezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/ICO-Pre-Sale.png  ICO Information  http://www.hubezoo.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/ICO-Factsheet.png  Get To Know Us!
